/Users/anthony/Programming/Deniable/docs/decisions/r3f-voxel-rendering.md:61:**Mesh-regen on destruction:** **O(1) per voxel changed.** Removing or relocating an instance is one `setMatrixAt` + `instanceMatrix.needsUpdate`. **<1 ms** for a typical RPG-size diff (200–1000 voxels). This is the pattern's standout strength.
