/Users/anthony/Programming/Deniable/sdp/verification/t-021@20260502t001433z-verify.md:68:{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:01:44.897Z","tool_name":"write_file","tool_id":"write_file_1777687304897_0","parameters":{"content":"# Verification Report — T-021 @sdp/verification/t-006@20260502t001433zd-verify.md\n\n**Verify Agent:** gemini-cli\n**Date:** 2026-05-01\n**Artifacts Reviewed:** `src/deniable/engine/activation.py`, `tests/test_engine_activation.py`, `src/deniable/engine/stats.py`\n\n## Correctness\nMet. The activation queue correctly alternates between sides and handles trailing units when one side has more units than the other. The Awareness token budget follows the `ceil(Resolve / 2)` formula (implemented as `(resolve + 1) // 2`). The `ACTIONS_PER_ACTIVATION` constant is set to 2 as required.\n\n## Completeness\nMet. The implementation covers all aspects of the task: alternating queue, drone slots, action count, and Awareness refresh. I added missing test coverage for trailing opponent activations and negative awareness spending to reach 100% coverage for `engine/activation.py`.\n\n## Consistency\nMet. The code follows the established project patterns (dataclasses, type hinting, StrEnum) and naming conventions. Tests are located in `tests/` and follow the `test_<module>.py` naming.\n\n## Security\nMet. No security vulnerabilities identified. The code uses standard Python types and logic. Input validation for stat ranges and awareness spending is present.\n\n## Quality\nMet. Code is clean, documented with docstrings, and has 100% test coverage for the target module. Overall project coverage is at 91.71%.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [x] (fixed) Missing coverage for trailing opponent activations in `next_activation`.\n- [x] (fixed) Missing coverage for negative spending in `spend_awareness`.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\n- Implementation is solid. Added two tests to `tests/test_engine_activation.py` to ensure 100% coverage of the activation logic.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-021 @20260502t001433z-verify.md"}}
