/Users/anthony/Programming/Deniable/sdp/verification/t-010@20260502t001433za-verify.md:67:One design note: `app = create_app()` at module level in `main.py` triggers `Settings()` at import time. If `DATABASE_URL` is absent from the environment, any import of `deniable.api.main` (or the compatibility `deniable.app`) fails. This is intentional per DN-004 ("missing required var causes clear startup error"), and `tests/conftest.py` handles it cleanly via `os.environ["DATABASE_URL"]` set before imports. Worth preserving this pattern as endpoints are added.
